## Product pricing

Products are priced differently depending on Product mode

## Regular products

Regular products can have their Price and Discount Price. The discount price can be enabled in the Product type editor Pricing tab and when filled, overwrites the Regular price.

In addition to this, the regular price can optionally be constructed [based on product add-ons](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_product-add-ons_.md)

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Variable products

When using Variable products mode, the price and discount price is added to each individual variation. Options to bulk copy and paste prices and other variation settings are available

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Booking products

Similar to Regular Products, Booking products can have a Base Price and Discount Price, and extended with add-ons. In addition to this, the Custom Prices module lets author overwrite prices of the booking product based on various conditions

![](data:image/png;base64,)
